Name: Frequency of SW-EIC Reject as the terminal activity in process variants
Percentage of process variants ending with SW-EIC Reject compared to all variants
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-EIC Reject' out of all cases

Name: Number of times SW-EIC Reject directly follows SW-Awaiting EIC Decision
Metric: Number of 'SW-EIC Reject' activities for cases where activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' occurs

Name: Percentage of SW-EIC Reject occurrences relative to the total number of activity executions in the log
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-EIC Reject' out of all cases

Name: Frequency of SW-EIC Reject in variants that include SW-Reviewer Agreed at least once
Metric: Frequency of activity 'SW-EIC Reject' for cases where activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' occurs

Name: Percentage of SW-EIC Reject cases where SW-Reviewer Agreed occurred earlier in the trace
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-EIC Reject' out of all 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Ratio of SW-EIC Reject to SW-EIC Accept across all completed review processes
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-EIC Reject' out of all 'SW-EIC Accept'

Name: Number of SW-EIC Reject decisions made after at least one reviewer agreed (i.e., after SW-Reviewer Agreed)
Metric: Number of 'SW-EIC Reject' activities for cases where activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' occurs

Name: Frequency of SW-EIC Reject in traces that never reached SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: Frequency of activity 'SW-EIC Reject' for cases where activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' does not occur

Name: Percentage of SW-EIC Reject occurring within 7 days after SW-Awaiting EIC Decision
Metric: the average of the function base < 7 where base is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'SW-EIC Reject' filtered by the function ma > 0 where ma is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Number of SW-EIC Reject instances in the initial submission phase (before any revision activities like RW-Initial Reviewer Selection)
Metric: Number of 'SW-EIC Reject' activities for cases where activity 'RW-Initial Reviewer Selection' does not occur

Name: Percentage of SW-EIC Reject in comparison to Immediate Reject Decision from the Checklist
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-EIC Reject' out of all 'Immediate Reject Decision from the Checklist'

Name: Frequency of SW-EIC Reject in variants with performance duration below the median case duration
Percentage of SW-EIC Reject out of all final editorial decisions (e.g., SW-EIC Accept, SW-EIC Major Revision, SW-EIC Minor Revision, SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit)
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'count': activity == 'SW-EIC Reject'", 'metric_condition': '> 0', 'aggregation': 'percentage', 'filter': "activity in ['SW-EIC Accept', 'SW-EIC Major Revision', 'SW-EIC Minor Revision', 'SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit', 'SW-EIC Reject']"}"

Name: Percentage of SW-EIC Reject among all EIC decision activities (including SW-EIC Accept, SW-EIC Major Revision, SW-EIC Minor Revision, SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit)
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'count': activity == 'SW-EIC Reject'", 'metric_condition': '> 0', 'aggregation': 'percentage', 'filter': "activity in ['SW-EIC Accept', 'SW-EIC Major Revision', 'SW-EIC Minor Revision', 'SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit', 'SW-EIC Reject']"}"
